OL,6,FA teenager was left with critical
OL,7,Finjuries after a hit-and-run involving
OL,8,Fa car seen speeding in Bradford.
OL,10,FWest Yorkshire Police said officers in
OL,11,Fa marked car saw the car driving at
OL,12,Fspeed on the opposite carriageway on
OL,13,FHalifax Road at about 8.25pm on Monday.
OL,15,FThey turned around to pursue the car
OL,16,Fbut lost sight of it.
